description: We specialize in fresh Maine lobster rolls! Our lobster is overnighted fresh daily. We also do other specials like Hawaiian chicken tacos, pork belly sandwiches, shrimp & crab BLT and more! We have catered weddings, birthday parties, housewarming parties, holiday parties, and several more large-scale events! We can serve any kind of menu- let us know a direction and we will go above and beyond to get there! :)
name: East Coast Joe's
